Class CompositeDateFormat

java.lang.Object
java.text.Format
java.text.DateFormat
net.greghaines.jesque.utils.CompositeDateFormat
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class CompositeDateFormat extends DateFormat
CompositeDateFormat attempts to parse dates using several known date format patterns and formats dates using ResqueDateFormatThreadLocal.getInstance().
Author:
Greg Haines
